'''提格雷战争'''（{{lang-ti|ውግእ ትግራይ}}）是自2020年11月4日起在[[埃塞俄比亚|埃塞俄比亚]]联邦政府和[[提格雷州|提格雷州]]政府之间发生的[[内战|内战]]<ref name=Reuters>{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-ethiopia-conflict/ethiopia-sends-army-into-tigray-region-heavy-fighting-reported-idUSKBN27K0ZS?il=0|title=Ethiopia sends army into Tigray region, heavy fighting reported|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2020-11-04|last1=Paravicini|first1=Giulia|last2=Endeshaw|first2=Dawit|accessdate=2020-11-04|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119083250/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-ethiopia-conflict/ethiopia-sends-army-into-tigray-region-heavy-fighting-reported-idUSKBN27K0ZS?il=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==事前態勢==
2020年9月9日，[[提格雷人民解放阵线|提格雷人民解放阵线]]执政的提格雷州无视埃塞俄比亚联邦政府推迟选举的命令<ref>{{Cite web |title=衣索比亞針對北方叛軍 進行非主動性戰爭 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202011060367.aspx |accessdate=2020-11-09 |author=徐梅玉 |date=2020-11-06 |publisher=中央通訊社 |language=zh-hant |location=約翰尼斯堡 |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129233700/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202011060367.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>，执意举行{{le|2020年提格雷地区选举|2020 Tigray regional election|地区选举}}。此后，早就已陷入不和状态的埃塞俄比亚联邦政府和提格雷人民解放阵线的关系急转直下。[[非洲联盟|非洲联盟]]尝试推动双方进行和平谈判，但是非盟的努力丝毫没起作用。埃塞俄比亚联邦政府认为，必须消除提格雷人民解放阵线对中央权力构成的威胁。随着局势日趋紧张，由埃塞俄比亚总理[[阿比·艾哈迈德|阿比·艾哈迈德]]任命的一个将军被提格雷州方面阻止履职<ref name=Bloomberg>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-11-04/ethiopia-prime-minister-orders-army-to-respond-to-tigray-attacks|title=Ethiopia Risks Descent Into Civil War as Tensions Flare|work=[[Bloomberg_News|Bloomberg]]|last1=Gebre|first1=Samuel|last2=Marks|first2=Simon|date=2020-11-04|accessdate=2020-11-06|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119083330/https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=e751ca30-2a41-11eb-801f-03955114db22&url=L25ld3MvYXJ0aWNsZXMvMjAyMC0xMS0wNC9ldGhpb3BpYS1wcmltZS1taW5pc3Rlci1vcmRlcnMtYXJteS10by1yZXNwb25kLXRvLXRpZ3JheS1hdHRhY2tz|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年11月3日，埃塞俄比亚[[联邦议会_(埃塞俄比亚)|联邦议会]]建议将提格雷人民解放阵线指定为[[恐怖组织|恐怖组织]]<ref name=BBC>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-54805088|title=Tigray crisis: Ethiopia orders military response after army base seized|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=2020-11-04|accessdate=2020-11-04|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119083309/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-54805088|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==武裝衝突==
===2020年===
2020年11月4日早上，埃塞俄比亚总理阿比·艾哈迈德在电视讲话中宣布，由于当日凌晨提格雷人民解放阵线袭击了[[埃塞俄比亚国防军|埃塞俄比亚国防军]]位于提格雷州的基地并试图占领北方司令部，国防军将在提格雷州开始对提格雷人民解放阵线发动军事进攻，并在提格雷州实施6个月[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref name="王柏文">{{Cite web |title=境內叛軍突襲 衣索比亞宣布緊急狀態 |url=https://news.pts.org.tw/article/499709 |accessdate=2020-11-10 |author=王柏文 |date=2020-11-10 |first=  |work=[[公視新聞|公視新聞]] |language=zh-hant}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=埃塞俄比亚在北部地区实施6个月紧急状态 |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/2020-11/04/c_1126698655.htm |accessdate=2020-11-09 |author=王守寶 |date=2020-11-04 |publisher=新華社 |language=zh-hans |location=亞的斯亞貝巴 |editor=王萌萌 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109132111/http://www.xinhuanet.com/2020-11/04/c_1126698655.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。提格雷州政府也宣布关闭领空，并声明驻扎当地的国防军已经归提格雷人民解放阵线指挥，但联邦政府对此表示否定。11月6日，阿比表示，针对提格雷人民解放阵线的第一轮军事行动已成功完成，埃塞俄比亚空军已成功歼灭了驻扎在各个战线的叛军的火箭炮和大炮，挫败了提格雷人民解放阵线使用火箭的意图，这些火箭可以击中提格雷州首府[[默克莱|默克莱]]300公里范围内的目标<ref>{{Cite web |title=埃塞俄比亚军队空袭该国前执政党军事目标 |url=https://world.huanqiu.com/article/40bTOGcwCGb |accessdate=2020-11-09 |date=2020-11-07 |work=環球網 |publisher=央視新聞 |language=zh-hans |editor=羅甜 |archive-date=2020-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114083349/https://world.huanqiu.com/article/40bTOGcwCGb |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在提格雷部隊對北方司令部的突襲中，埃軍有大量武器被奪取，部分軍官和士兵投向提格雷一方，另有數以千計的埃軍軍官和士兵被殺或被俘<ref name=bbc20211118>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-59288744 |title=Ethiopia's Tigray conflict: How the TPLF has outflanked the army |publisher=BBC |date=2021-11-18 |accessdate=2021-11-21 |archive-date=2021-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211201164331/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-59288744 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年11月7日，埃塞俄比亚联邦议会联邦院通过决议，废除提格雷州现有议会和行政机构，成立{{le|提格雷过渡政府|Transitional Government of Tigray|过渡政府}}，由过渡政府重新任命行政机构成员。过渡政府将获授权举行选举，并执行联邦政府通过的决定<ref>{{Cite web |title=埃塞俄比亚议会上院通过决议在提格雷州组建过渡政府 |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2020-11/08/c_1126711462.htm |accessdate=2020-11-09 |author=王守寶 |date=2020-11-08 |publisher=新華社 |language=zh-hans |editor=錢中兵 |location=亞的斯亞貝巴 |archive-date=2020-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117140336/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2020-11/08/c_1126711462.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

冲突引发该地数万人逃亡苏丹等国<ref>{{cite web |title=埃塞俄比亚北部冲突引发20年来最大难民潮 联合国正在边境地区加大援助 |url=https://news.un.org/zh/story/2020/11/1071892 |website=联合国新闻 |access-date=2020-11-19 |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127111735/https://news.un.org/zh/story/2020/11/1071892 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。提人阵武装还对[[厄立特里亚|厄立特里亚]]首都[[阿斯马拉|阿斯马拉]]发动火箭弹袭击<ref>{{cite web |title=埃塞战火升级：提人阵对厄立特里亚首都发火箭弹，更多国家恐卷入 |url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/5275954.html |website=界面新闻 |access-date=2020-11-19 |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127185932/https://www.jiemian.com/article/5275954.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年11月28日，埃塞俄比亚总理阿比和国防军总参谋长朱拉通过社交媒体表示埃塞俄比亚军队已经全面控制提格雷州的首府[[默克莱|默克莱]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/ethiopian-military-in-full-control-20201128/5679993.html |title=埃塞俄比亚军队全面控制提格雷地区首府 |access-date=2020-11-28 |archive-date=2020-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214131136/https://www.voachinese.com/a/ethiopian-military-in-full-control-20201128/5679993.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。朱拉表示埃軍釋放了早前被提格雷部隊拘留的7,000名國防軍成員<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2020-11/29/c_1126798464.htm |title=埃塞俄比亚国防军控制北部提格雷州首府 |publisher=新華網 |date=2020-11-29 |accessdate=2021-12-02 |archive-date=2021-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211202053517/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2020-11/29/c_1126798464.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===2021年===
2021年4月，[[埃塞俄比亞正統合性教會|埃塞俄比亞正統合性教會]]牧首[[阿布纳·马蒂亚斯|阿布纳·马蒂亚斯]]指稱提格雷正在發生[[种族灭绝|种族灭绝]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2021/05/08/africa/orthodox-church-tigray-ethiopia-intl/index.html |title=Ethiopian Orthodox Church Patriarch condemns Tigray 'genocide' |publisher=CNN |date=2021-05-08 |accessdate=2021-05-09 |archive-date=2021-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210530223639/https://edition.cnn.com/2021/05/08/africa/orthodox-church-tigray-ethiopia-intl/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.voanews.com/africa/ethiopian-orthodox-church-patriarch-blasts-tigray-genocide |title=Ethiopian Orthodox Church Patriarch Blasts Tigray 'Genocide' |website=VOA |date=2021-05-09 |accessdate=2021-05-09 |archive-date=2021-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513111316/https://www.voanews.com/africa/ethiopian-orthodox-church-patriarch-blasts-tigray-genocide |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月13日，埃塞俄比亞国防军称已消灭提格雷州8个地区的提人阵军政府组织<ref name=消滅>{{cite news |title=埃塞俄比亚联邦政府将提格雷人民解放阵线和奥罗莫解放阵线/谢恩列为恐怖组织 |url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2021-05-01/doc-ikmxzfmm0112606.shtml |accessdate=2021-08-12 |archive-date=2021-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501143625/https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2021-05-01/doc-ikmxzfmm0112606.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據報在戰爭開始後，埃塞俄比亞當局拘留了超過17,000名在埃軍服役的提格雷尼亞人<ref>{{cite news |url=https://apnews.com/article/africa-ethiopia-race-and-ethnicity-health-coronavirus-5f22a5aea128cbd659fbf4f810aac973 |script-title=en:‘Clean out our insides’: Ethiopia detains Tigrayans amid war |work=AP News |date=2021-04-29 |accessdate=2021-11-04 |archive-date=2021-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211205223251/https://apnews.com/article/africa-ethiopia-race-and-ethnicity-health-coronavirus-5f22a5aea128cbd659fbf4f810aac973 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2021年5月，埃塞俄比亞政府把提人陣和奥罗莫解放阵线/谢恩列為[[恐怖組織|恐怖組織]]<ref name=消滅/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theafricareport.com/99330/ethiopia-victory-for-the-oromo-will-come-from-winning-hearts-and-minds-not-terrorising-people/ |title=Ethiopia: Victory for the Oromo will come from winning hearts and minds, not terrorising people |website=theafricareport.com |date=2021-06-18 |access-date=2021-08-10 |archive-date=2021-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210808041418/https://www.theafricareport.com/99330/ethiopia-victory-for-the-oromo-will-come-from-winning-hearts-and-minds-not-terrorising-people/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2021年6月10日，聯合國一名官員表示提格雷已發生[[饑荒|饑荒]]。6月11日，有報導引用比利時[[根特大學|根特大學]]研究員的「提格雷人道地圖集」，指出在提格雷的600萬人口中，只有三分之一人住在埃塞俄比亞政府控制區，另外三分之一人住在厄立特里亞軍控制區，另外150萬人住在提格雷叛軍控制的鄉郊地區。曾在該地區一些農業項目工作的一個根特大學團隊表示當地有大片農田因為農民缺乏種子、耕牛或肥料而被棄耕，更甚的是有士兵威嚇當地農民不得耕種，一些偏遠村莊的農民只能在黑夜偷偷走到田裏犁地<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-57422168 |title=Ethiopia's Tigray crisis: Tragedy of the man-made famine |publisher=BBC |date=2021-06-11 |accessdate=2021-06-11 |archive-date=2021-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210629163742/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-57422168 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。6月中旬，歐盟提格雷問題特使、[[芬兰外交部|芬蘭外長]][[佩卡·哈維斯托|佩卡·哈維斯托]]稱他在2月與埃塞俄比亞領導層會面時，對方有人說出他們要摧毀提格雷尼亞人，在100年裡徹底消滅提格雷尼亞人之類的話<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/6/18/ethiopian-leaders-said-they-would-wipe-out-tigrayans-eu-envoy |script-title=en:Ethiopian leaders said they would ‘wipe out’ Tigrayans: EU envoy |website=aljazeera.com |date=2021-06-18 |accessdate=2021-07-01 |archive-date=2021-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210630163219/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/6/18/ethiopian-leaders-said-they-would-wipe-out-tigrayans-eu-envoy |dead-url=no }}</ref>。6月28日，提格雷叛軍收復提格雷州首府[[默克萊|默克萊]]，大批居民上街慶祝。埃塞俄比亞政府同日單方面宣布在提格雷州實施停火直至耕作季節結束<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-57645282 |title=Ethiopia's Tigray conflict: Unilateral ceasefire declared |publisher=BBC |date=2021-06-28 |accessdate=2021-06-29 |archive-date=2021-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210701175732/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-57645282 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/06/28/world/asia/tigray-mekelle-ethiopia-retreat.html |title=Ethiopian Forces Retreat in Tigray, and Rebels Enter the Capital |publisher=The New York Times |date=2021-06-28 |accessdate=2021-06-29 |archive-date=2021-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210701083833/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/06/28/world/asia/tigray-mekelle-ethiopia-retreat.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。6月29日，厄立特里亞軍撤離{{link-en|希雷 (埃塞俄比亞)|Shire Inda Selassie|希雷}}、[[阿克蘇姆|阿克蘇姆]]和[[阿杜瓦|阿杜瓦]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/world/ethiopia-tigray-ceasefire-1.6084930 |title=Eritrean forces withdraw from key towns in Ethiopia's Tigray 1 day after declaration of ceasefire |website=cbc.ca |date=2021-06-29 |accessdate=2021-07-01 |archive-date=2021-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210701013123/https://www.cbc.ca/news/world/ethiopia-tigray-ceasefire-1.6084930 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。叛軍宣稱在6月攻勢中消滅數萬名埃軍<ref name=bbc20210703/>。

2021年7月1日，提人陣主席[[德布雷齐翁·格布雷迈克尔|德布雷齐翁·格布雷迈克尔]]接受《紐約時報》訪問時宣稱提格雷一方在戰爭初期受到阿比政府的盟友[[阿拉伯联合酋长国|阿聯酋]]的無人機攻擊<ref name=nyt20210704>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/03/world/africa/tigray-leader-interview-ethiopia.html |script-title=en:‘I Didn’t Expect to Make It Back Alive’: An Interview With Tigray’s Leader |publisher=The New York Times |date=2021-07-04 |accessdate=2021-07-05 |archive-date=2021-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210804162812/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/03/world/africa/tigray-leader-interview-ethiopia.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。7月2日，提格雷叛軍將數千名埃軍戰俘帶到默克萊遊街示眾，一些戰俘躺在擔架床上由他人抬著，另外一些戰俘綁着染血繃帶。提格雷方面表示他們將會釋放戰俘中的低階士兵，而軍官則繼續拘留<ref name=nyt20210702>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/02/world/africa/tigray-ethiopia-soldiers-captured.html |title=After Sudden Defeat, Captured Ethiopian Soldiers Are Marched to Prison |publisher=The New York Times |date=2021-07-02 |accessdate=2021-07-03 |archive-date=2021-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210730105750/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/02/world/africa/tigray-ethiopia-soldiers-captured.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。7月6日起，提格雷政府开始动员，准备从阿姆哈拉民兵手中夺回西提格雷。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tigray forces mobilise against militias from neighbouring province|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jul/06/tigray-forces-mobilise-against-militias-from-neighbouring-province|access-date=2021-07-06|date=2021-07-06|last=Burke|first=Jason|website=The Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2021-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210804105131/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jul/06/tigray-forces-mobilise-against-militias-from-neighbouring-province|dead-url=no}}</ref>7月12日，提格雷防卫力量发起了一波攻势。提格雷军占领了南提格雷，包括阿拉马塔和科雷姆。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rebel forces in Ethiopia's Tigray region launch new offensive|url=https://www.france24.com/en/africa/20210713-rebel-forces-in-ethiopia-s-tigray-region-launch-new-offensive|access-date=2021-07-13|date=2021-07-13|website=France 24|language=en|archive-date=2021-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210722125144/https://www.france24.com/en/africa/20210713-rebel-forces-in-ethiopia-s-tigray-region-launch-new-offensive|dead-url=no}}</ref> 提格雷防卫力量随后越过[[特克澤河|特克澤河]]西征佔領麦·泽布里，迫使[[阿姆哈拉州|阿姆哈拉州]]當局著手大規模動員民兵<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ethiopia: Tigray forces push south as Amhara militias mobilise|url=https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/un-rights-council-passes-resolution-calling-eritrean-troop-withdrawal-tigray-2021-07-13/|access-date=2021-07-13|date=2021-07-13|last=Mersie|first=Ayenat|website=Reuters|last2=Fick|first2=Maggie|archive-date=2021-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210730053736/https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/un-rights-council-passes-resolution-calling-eritrean-troop-withdrawal-tigray-2021-07-13/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在提格雷防卫力量迅猛进军下，艾哈迈德总理威胁要恢复与提格雷的战争并镇压叛乱者，这引起了人们对于种族屠杀的恐慌。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Collins|first=Tom|date=2021-07-19|title=Genocide fears after Ethiopian PM vows to crush ‘weeds’ of Tigray|language=en|work=The Times|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/abiys-pledge-to-crush-weeds-of-tigray-raises-fears-of-genocide-in-ethiopia-sx0xkqb2v|access-date=2021-07-22|issn=0140-0460|archive-date=2021-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210724000659/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/abiys-pledge-to-crush-weeds-of-tigray-raises-fears-of-genocide-in-ethiopia-sx0xkqb2v|dead-url=no}}</ref>他召唤了埃塞俄比亚其他地区的民兵组织，[[奧羅米亞州|奥罗米亚]]、[[錫達馬州|锡达玛]]以及[[南方民族、部落和人民州|南方州]]响应了艾哈迈德的号召并动员了起来。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ethiopia regions send troops to back fight with Tigray rebels|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/7/15/ethiopia-regions-send-troops-to-back-fight-with-tigray-rebels|access-date=2021-07-22|date=2021-07-15|website=Al Jazeera|language=en|archive-date=2021-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210803135339/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/7/15/ethiopia-regions-send-troops-to-back-fight-with-tigray-rebels|dead-url=no}}</ref>作为回应，提格雷防卫力量入侵了毗邻的[[阿法尔州|阿法尔州]]，迫使[[本尚古勒-古馬茲州|本尚古勒-古马兹州]]、[[甘貝拉州|甘贝拉州]]、[[哈勒爾州|哈勒尔州]]以及[[索馬里州|索马里州]]也参与到战争之中。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ethiopia's Tigray forces enter neighbouring Afar region, Afar says|url=https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/ethiopias-tigray-forces-enter-neighbouring-afar-region-afar-says-2021-07-19/|access-date=2021-07-22|date=2021-07-19|last=Endeshaw|first=Dawit|website=Reuters|last2=Flick|first2=Maggie|archive-date=2021-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210730041126/https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/ethiopias-tigray-forces-enter-neighbouring-afar-region-afar-says-2021-07-19/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在阿法尔西部的激烈交火已经导致了54,000余人离家失所，据传闻提格雷防卫力量占领了该州的三个区。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tigray: thousands flee in neighbouring region as conflict spreads|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jul/22/ethiopia-tigray-thousands-flee-in-neighbouring-region-as-conflict-spreads|access-date=2021-07-22|date=2021-07-22|website=The Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2021-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210804124937/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jul/22/ethiopia-tigray-thousands-flee-in-neighbouring-region-as-conflict-spreads|dead-url=no}}</ref>尽管[[提格雷人民解放阵线|提人阵]]声称其进入阿法尔的目标仅仅是联邦军队，专家们相信他们的目标是占领[[恩贾梅纳－吉布提高速公路|恩贾梅纳－吉布提高速公路]]，这是埃塞俄比亚一条重要的贸易路线，与[[吉布提港|吉布提港]]相连。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Nunis|first=Vivienne|date=2021-07-22|title=Ethiopia Tigray crisis: New front opens in war as aid fears grow|language=en-GB|work=BBC|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-57926832|access-date=2021-07-22|archive-date=2021-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210728155915/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-57926832|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Djiboutian troops close in to Ethiopia as TDF allegedly targets transport corridor|url=https://www.garoweonline.com/en/world/africa/djiboutian-troops-close-in-to-ethiopia-as-tdf-allegedly-targets-transport-corridor|access-date=2021-07-22|date=2021-07-21|website=Garowe Online|language=en|archive-date=2021-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210722212808/https://www.garoweonline.com/en/world/africa/djiboutian-troops-close-in-to-ethiopia-as-tdf-allegedly-targets-transport-corridor|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年8月5日，提格雷軍攻佔[[拉利貝拉|拉利貝拉]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-58101912 |title=Lalibela: Ethiopia's Tigray rebels take Unesco world heritage town |publisher=BBC |date=2021-08-04 |accessdate=2021-08-06 |archive-date=2021-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210826110245/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-58101912 |dead-url=no }}</ref>8月11日，「奧羅莫解放軍」領導人向美聯社表示早前已與提人陣達成協議，合組軍事聯盟對抗阿比政府。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.voanews.com/africa/ethiopia-armed-group-says-it-has-alliance-tigray-forces |title=Ethiopia Armed Group Says it Has Alliance with Tigray Forces |website=VOA |date=2021-08-11 |accessdate=2021-08-11 |archive-date=2021-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210811113855/https://www.voanews.com/africa/ethiopia-armed-group-says-it-has-alliance-tigray-forces |dead-url=no }}</ref>

