t-forces-in-control-of-chifra-state-media |title=Ethiopian gov’t forces in control of Chifra: State media |publisher=Al Jazeera |date=2021-11-28 |accessdate=2021-11-29 |archive-date=2021-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211216110813/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/11/28/ethiopian-government-forces-in-control-of-chifra-state-media |dead-url=no }}</ref>

