e news |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/12/18/ethiopia-claims-retaking-towns-from-tigray-rebels |title=Ethiopia forces claim recapturing of towns from Tigray rebels |website=Al Jazeera |date=2021-12-18}}</ref>12月20日，提人陣宣佈已完成從阿姆哈拉州和阿法爾州撤軍。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/12/20/tplf-rebels-announce-retreat-to-ethiopias-tigray-region |title=Tigrayan forces announce retreat to Ethiopia’s Tigray region |publisher=Al Jazeera |date=2021-12-21 |accessdate=2021-12-31 |archive-date=2021-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211229204925/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/12/20/tplf-rebels-announce-retreat-to-ethiopias-tigray-region }}</ref>12月23日，埃塞俄比亞政府宣佈已命令軍隊停止在提格雷州境內推進。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/12/24/ethiopia-govt-says-army-will-not-go-deeper-into-tigray-for-now |script-title=en:Ethiopia gov’t says army will not go deeper into Tigray, for now |publisher=Al Jazeera |date=2021-12-24 |accessdate=2021-12-31 |archive-date=2022-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220524124114/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/12/24/ethiopia-govt-says-army-will-not-go-deeper-into-tigray-for-now }}</ref>

== 戰術 ==
提格雷戰爭的交戰雙方均被指使用了[[人海戰術|人海戰術]]。[[埃塞俄比亚|埃塞俄比亚]]政府指責[[提格雷人民解放陣線|提格雷人民解放陣線]]把平民推上前線實施人海戰術，並指中央政府一方也可以採用人海戰術對付人海戰術。{{le|艾力克斯·德·瓦爾|Alex de Waal}}宣稱中央政府一方自2021年6月大敗後實施人海戰術。Martin Plaut宣稱中央政府一方把大量訓練不足的士兵投入戰場，以人海戰術試圖突破提格雷軍戰線。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://martinplaut.com/2021/10/17/a-decisive-moment-in-the-war-in-tigray-a-best-guess-at-the-outcome/ |title=A decisive moment in the war in Tigray – a “best guess” at the outcome |date=2021-10-17 |author=Martin Plaut |access-date=2021-11-12 |archive-date=2021-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112062314/https://martinplaut.com/2021/10/17/a-decisive-moment-in-the-war-in-tigray-a-best-guess-at-the-outcome/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.aa.com.tr/en/africa/ethiopia-launches-airstrikes-on-tigray-capital-rebels-claim-3-civilians-killed/2396785 |title=Ethiopia launches airstrikes on Tigray capital, rebels claim 3 civilians killed |website=aa.com.tr |date=2021-10-19 |accessdate=2021-11-12 |archive-date=2021-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112062309/https://www.aa.com.tr/en/africa/ethiopia-launches-airstrikes-on-tigray-capital-rebels-claim-3-civilians-killed/2396785 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://sites.tufts.edu/reinventingpeace/2021/11/08/what-next-for-ethiopia/ |title=What Next for Ethiopia? |author=Alex DeWaal |date=2021-11-08 |access-date=2021-11-12 |archive-date=2021-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211130032544/https://sites.tufts.edu/reinventingpeace/2021/11/08/what-next-for-ethiopia/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>據報有些時候進行第二波衝鋒的埃軍士兵根本沒有槍，有數以千計甚至可能萬計的士兵在人海戰術中陣亡。Ann Fitz-Gerald相信同樣採用人海戰術的提格雷軍傷亡更慘重。<ref name=bbc20211118/>

== 战争罪 ==
在提格雷战争中，许多来源指出[[埃塞俄比亚|埃塞俄比亚政府军]]和[[提格雷州|提格雷]]叛军都犯下了不同程度的[[战争罪|战争罪]]。

=== 人造饥荒 ===
自战争开始，埃塞俄比亚政府就切断了提格雷地区的对外交流。<ref>{{Cite web|title=There’s a brutal conflict in Ethiopia. My family there ask: why does no one hear us?|url=https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2021/nov/17/conflict-ethiopia-tigray-war-starving|access-date=2022-03-05|author=Magdalene Abraha|date=2021-11-17|work=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2022-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220605083415/https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2021/nov/17/conflict-ethiopia-tigray-war-starving}}</ref> 同时，战争和[[蝗災|蝗灾]]导致地区收成受损。因为收成短缺以及无法进口食品，提格雷地区目前正在经历大规模的[[饑荒|饥荒]]。截至2021年5月，提格雷有550万人面临严重的粮食短缺，超过35,0000人经历灾难性饥荒。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ipcinfo.org/fileadmin/user_upload/ipcinfo/docs/IPC_Ethiopia_Acute_Food_Insecurity_2021MaySept_national.pdf|title=5.5 Million People in Tigray and Neighbouring Zones of Afar and Amhara Face High Levels of Acute Food Insecurity|date=June 2021|publisher=[[Integrated_Food_Security_Phase_Classification|Integrated Food Security Phase Classification]]|access-date=2022-03-06|archive-date=2022-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220127123219/https://www.ipcinfo.org/fileadmin/user_upload/ipcinfo/docs/IPC_Ethiopia_Acute_Food_Insecurity_2021MaySept_national.pdf}}</ref><ref name="aljaz_2021">{{Cite web|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/6/10/un-official-says-350000-people-in-famine-in-ethiopias-tigray|title=350,000 people in famine conditions in Ethiopia's Tigray|website=[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]|date=10 June 2021|access-date=2022-03-06|archive-date=2022-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220330225410/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/6/10/un-official-says-350000-people-in-famine-in-ethiopias-tigray}}</ref>这是自2011年[[索马里饥荒|索马里饥荒]]以来全世界最严重的一场饥荒。<ref name="aljaz_2021" />

根据[[经济学人|《经济学人》]]的报道，[[埃塞俄比亚|埃塞俄比亚政府]]正在故意阻止食物进入提格雷，试图通过饥荒让叛军投降。<ref name=":0">{{cite news |title= After two months of war, Tigray faces starvation – Ethiopia's government appears to be blocking food deliveries to the region |date= 23 January 2021 |newspaper= [[The_Economist|The Economist]] |url= https://www.economist.com/middle-east-and-africa/2021/01/23/after-two-months-of-war-tigray-faces-starvation |access-date= 11 February 2021 |archive-url= https://archive.today/20210122115938/https://www.economist.com/middle-east-and-africa/2021/01/23/after-two-months-of-war-tigray-faces-starvation |archive-date= 2021-01-22 |url-status= live }}</ref>埃塞俄比亚政府在2021年1月底否认了这一说法。<ref name=":0" />同年2月10日，埃塞俄比亚[[红十字会|红十字会]]的负责人表示许多到达达格雷安镇的营地的难民“瘦弱”到“真的皮包骨头”的样子。他估计人道主义援助无法到达提格雷“百分之八十”的人口。<ref name=":1">{{cite news | title= Ethiopian Red Cross says 80 percent of Tigray cut off from aid | date= 10 February 2021 | agency= [[Agence_France_Presse|AFP]] | newspaper= [[France_24|France 24]] | url= https://www.france24.com/en/live-news/20210210-ethiopian-red-cross-says-80-percent-of-tigray-cut-off-from-aid | access-date= 10 February 2021 | archive-url= https://archive.today/20210210200846/https://www.france24.com/en/live-news/20210210-ethiopian-red-cross-says-80-percent-of-tigray-cut-off-from-aid | archive-date= 2021-02-10 | url-status= live }}</ref>2021年2月埃塞俄比亚和平部长允许增加在格雷地区的粮食分配。<ref name=":1" />

=== [[战争时期的性暴力|战时强奸]] ===
提格雷战争中的交战双方都有大规模[[强奸|强奸]]、[[輪姦|轮奸]]和虐待平民妇女的行为。<ref name=":4">{{Citation|title=Ethiopia's Tigray conflict: Rape as a weapon of war {{!}} DW {{!}} 26.02.2022|url=https://www.dw.com/en/ethiopias-tigray-conflict-rape-as-a-weapon-of-war/av-60857552|accessdate=2022-03-05|language=en-GB|first=|last=|publisher=德国之声|archive-date=2022-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220401032705/https://www.dw.com/en/ethiopias-tigray-conflict-rape-as-a-weapon-of-war/av-60857552}}</ref>许多士兵和民兵对当地妇女（包括孕妇和小至7岁的女孩）进行强奸、轮奸、[[性奴隸|性奴役]]、性残割和其他形式的[[性虐待|性虐待]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ethiopia: Troops and militia rape, abduct women and girls in Tigray conflict – new report|url=https://www.amnesty.org/en/latest/news/2021/08/ethiopia-troops-and-militia-rape-abduct-women-and-girls-in-tigray-conflict-new-report/|access-date=2022-03-05|date=2021-08-10|work=Amnesty International|language=en|archive-date=2022-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220627025117/https://www.amnesty.org/en/latest/news/2021/08/ethiopia-troops-and-militia-rape-abduct-women-and-girls-in-tigray-conflict-new-report/}}</ref>这些性虐待还常常伴随着其他生理性和心理性的施虐。生理施虐包括用滚烫的铁片或者香烟头灼伤受害者，往受害者[[阴道|阴道]]里塞入铁棍、铁钉等异物，用锐器戳伤受害者等。<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Ethiopia: “I don’t know if they realized I was a person”: Rape and sexual violence in the conflict in Tigray, Ethiopia|url=https://www.amnesty.org/en/documents/afr25/4569/2021/en/|access-date=2022-03-05|work=Amnesty International|language=en|archive-date=2022-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220619180617/https://www.amnesty.org/en/documents/afr25/4569/2021/en/}}</ref>心理施虐包括在受害者家属甚至孩子面前强奸他们、强迫受害者和家庭成员[[近親性交|乱伦]]、言语羞辱或侮辱受害者等。<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=United Nations Special Representative of the Secretary-General on Sexual Violence in Conflict, Ms. Pramila Patten, urges all parties to prohibit the use of sexual violence and cease hostilities in the Tigray region of Ethiopia|url=https://www.un.org/sexualviolenceinconflict/press-release/united-nations-special-representative-of-the-secretary-general-on-sexual-violence-in-conflict-ms-pramila-patten-urges-all-parties-to-prohibit-the-use-of-sexual-violence-and-cease-hostilities-in-the/|access-date=2022-03-05|last=Boezio|first=Geraldine|work=United Nations Office of the Special Representative of the Secretary-General on Sexual Violence in Conflict|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220428042724/https://www.un.org/sexualviolenceinconflict/press-release/united-nations-special-representative-of-the-secretary-general-on-sexual-violence-in-conflict-ms-pramila-patten-urges-all-parties-to-prohibit-the-use-of-sexual-violence-and-cease-hostilities-in-the/}}</ref>在被强奸之后，很多受害者会感染[[艾滋病|艾滋病]]等[[性傳染病|性传染病]]。然而因为战时医疗资源的匮乏和受害者的[[羞耻|羞耻心]]，很多受害者都无法及时得到治疗。<ref name=":2" />

截至2021年8月，在医院登记的强奸受害者数量有512-516名，<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|title=Men forced to rape family members in Ethiopia’s Tigray region, says UN|url=https://www.irishtimes.com/news/world/africa/men-forced-to-rape-family-members-in-ethiopia-s-tigray-region-says-un-1.4520903|access-date=2022-03-05|work=The Irish Times|language=en|archive-date=2022-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324163435/https://www.irishtimes.com/news/world/africa/men-forced-to-rape-family-members-in-ethiopia-s-tigray-region-says-un-1.4520903}}</ref><ref name=":5">{{Cite news|title=‘We’re here to make you HIV positive’: Hundreds of women rush to Tigray hospitals as soldiers use rape as weapon of war|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/global-health/women-and-girls/make-hiv-positive-hundreds-women-rush-tigray-hospitals-soldiers/|newspaper=The Telegraph|date=2021-03-27|accessdate=2022-03-05|issn=0307-1235|language=en-GB|first=Lucy|last=Kassa|first2=Anna|last2=Pujol-Mazzini|archive-date=2022-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220524032022/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/global-health/women-and-girls/make-hiv-positive-hundreds-women-rush-tigray-hospitals-soldiers/}}</ref>但实际数字应该远高于此。英国议员海伦·海斯估计提格雷战争中的强奸案更接近10,000起。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Conflict in Tigray Region of Ethiopia|url=https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2021-03-25/debates/5D6EC59D-4744-425B-8086-2C13256A34ED/ConflictInTigrayRegionOfEthiopia|author=Helen Hayes|publisher=英国议会|access-date=2022-03-06|archive-date=2022-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220331163819/https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2021-03-25/debates/5D6EC59D-4744-425B-8086-2C13256A34ED/ConflictInTigrayRegionOfEthiopia}}</ref>而[[联合国人口基金|联合国人口基金]]估计埃塞俄比亚目前有26,000名妇女需要[[性暴力|性暴力]]后医疗和心理服务。<ref>{{Cite web|title=UNFPA Ethiopia Response to the Tigray Crisis - Situation report|url=https://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/UNFPA%20Ethiopia%20Response%20to%20the%20Tigray%20Crisis%20-%20Situation%20report%20(15%20to%2030%20June%202021).pdf|publisher=UNFPA|access-date=2022-03-06|archive-date=2022-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220417144111/https://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/UNFPA%20Ethiopia%20Response%20to%20the%20Tigray%20Crisis%20-%20Situation%20report%20(15%20to%2030%20June%202021).pdf}}</ref>许多来源都认为提格雷地区的大规模强奸是有计划的战略行为，旨在破坏敌方的士气、对敌方民族进行[[种族灭绝式强奸|种族灭绝式强奸]]以及在敌方领土散布[[艾滋病|艾滋病]]以进行[[细菌战|生化战]]。<ref name=":4" /><ref name=":5" />

=== 反人类罪 ===
埃塞俄比亚人权委员会在2020年11月声称埃塞俄比亚在[[迈卡德拉大屠杀|迈卡德拉]]的屠杀“可能”构成[[危害人类罪|反人类罪]]。2020年11月28日，埃塞俄比亚政府军在[[阿克蘇姆|阿克苏姆]]市屠杀了800平民。<ref>{{Citation|title=Killings in Axum by Eritrea troops ‘may amount to war crimes’|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RNEflsY3U3w|accessdate=2022-03-06|language=en|publisher=半岛电视台|archive-date=2022-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220306041304/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RNEflsY3U3w}}</ref>[[國際特赦組織|国际特赦组织]]在报告中宣布阿克苏姆地区的屠杀可能“构成战争罪”。

=== 种族灭绝 ===
许多来源指责[[埃塞俄比亚|埃塞俄比亚]]和[[厄立特里亚|厄立特里亚]]政府对提格雷人进行[[种族清洗|种族清洗]]和[[种族灭绝|灭绝]]。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Ethiopia’s War Leads to Ethnic Cleansing in Tigray Region, U.S. Report Says|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/02/26/world/middleeast/ethiopia-tigray-ethnic-cleansing.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2021-02-26|accessdate=2022-03-06|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Declan|last=Walsh|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://archive.today/20210226235751/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/02/26/world/middleeast/ethiopia-tigray-ethnic-cleansing.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title='Leave no Tigrayan': In Ethiopia, an ethnicity is erased|url=https://apnews.com/article/ethiopia-tigray-minority-ethnic-cleansing-sudan-world-news-842741eebf9bf0984946619c0fc15023|access-date=2022-03-06|date=2021-04-26|work=AP NEWS|language=en|archive-date=2022-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220621235714/https://apnews.com/article/ethiopia-tigray-minority-ethnic-cleansing-sudan-world-news-842741eebf9bf0984946619c0fc15023}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Blinken: Acts of 'ethnic cleansing' committed in Western Tigray|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/03/10/politics/blinken-tigray-ethnic-cleansing/index.html|access-date=2022-03-06|last=CNN|first=Jennifer Hansler|work=CNN|archive-date=2022-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220420164544/https://www.cnn.com/2021/03/10/politics/blinken-tigray-ethnic-cleansing/index.html}}</ref>[[种族灭绝观察|种族灭绝观察]]宣布埃塞俄比亚的种族灭绝已经进行到了第9步-根除，以及第10步-否认。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Timestreams|url=https://www.genocidewatch.com/timestreams|access-date=2022-03-06|work=genocidewatch|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220423211333/https://www.genocidewatch.com/timestreams}}</ref>据[[欧洲联盟|欧盟]]驻埃塞俄比亚特使佩卡·哈维斯托称，埃塞俄比亚政府高级官员正在呼吁“消灭”所有提格雷人。<ref>{{Cite web|title=EU envoy: Ethiopian leadership vowed to 'wipe out' Tigrayans|url=https://apnews.com/article/europe-ethiopia-africa-ffd3dc3faf15d0501fd87cafe274e65a|access-date=2022-03-06|date=2021-06-18|work=AP NEWS|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220416005424/https://apnews.com/article/europe-ethiopia-africa-ffd3dc3faf15d0501fd87cafe274e65a}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Ethiopian leaders said they would ‘wipe out’ Tigrayans: EU envoy|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/6/18/ethiopian-leaders-said-they-would-wipe-out-tigrayans-eu-envoy|access-date=2022-03-06|work=www.aljazeera.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210630163219/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/6/18/ethiopian-leaders-said-they-would-wipe-out-tigrayans-eu-envoy}}</ref>埃塞俄比亚政府否认了这些指控。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Ethiopia rejects U.S. allegations of ethnic cleansing in Tigray|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/uk-ethiopia-conflict-idUSKBN2B50ES|newspaper=Reuters|date=2021-03-13|accessdate=2022-03-06|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211031063729/https://www.reuters.com/article/uk-ethiopia-conflict-idUSKBN2B50ES}}</ref>

== 人道主义危机 ==
根据联合国的数据，约有230万左右的儿童无法获得急需的援助和人道主义救助。自从本次纷争开始起，埃塞俄比亚联邦政府一直严格控制着提格雷地区的进出，[[联合国儿童基金会|联合国儿童基金会]]称，埃塞俄比亚政府仍未能确保足够的“粮食、包括用来治疗儿童营养不良的即用医疗粮食，药品、水、燃料以及其他正在枯竭的必需品。”<ref name="UNICEF_1">{{cite web|title=Millions of children in Tigray remain out of reach, despite access agreement – UNICEF|url=https://www.unicef.org/press-releases/millions-children-tigray-remain-out-reach-despite-access-agreement-unicef|access-date=2020-12-17|date=2020-12-15|website=[[UNICEF|UNICEF]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217170619/https://www.unicef.org/press-releases/millions-children-tigray-remain-out-reach-despite-access-agreement-unicef|archive-date=2020-12-17|url-status=no}}</ref><ref name="YahooNews_1">{{cite web|title=UN 'frustration' at lack of access to Tigray|url=https://news.yahoo.com/un-frustration-lack-access-tigray-190020612.html|access-date=2020-12-17|date=2020-12-15|website=[[Yahoo!_News|Yahoo! News]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216141042/https://news.yahoo.com/un-frustration-lack-access-tigray-190020612.html|archive-date=2020-12-16|url-status=no}}</ref><ref name="BBC_N_1">{{cite web|title=Ethiopia's Tigray crisis: About 2.3 million children cut off from aid, UN says|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-55327559?fbclid=IwAR1EZi-YMGiFdAxHG_N2bxflP8XoyJN81vaM1zHvFIa5YhBiDacEY6My9cM|access-date=2020-12-17|date=2020-12-15|website=[[BBC|BBC]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131225001/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-55327559?fbclid=IwAR1EZi-YMGiFdAxHG_N2bxflP8XoyJN81vaM1zHvFIa5YhBiDacEY6My9cM|archive-date=2021-01-31|url-status=no}}</ref><ref name="CNN_ref_1">{{cite web|title=More than two million children in Ethiopia's Tigray region cut off from humanitarian aid, UN says|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/12/16/africa/ethiopia-tigray-un-children-humanitarian-aid-intl/index.html|date=2020-12-15|website=[[CNN|CNN]]|last1=McSweeney|first1=Eoin|access-date=2021-07-28|archive-date=2021-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211031020819/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/12/16/africa/ethiopia-tigray-un-children-humanitarian-aid-intl/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Deutsche_Welle_1">{{cite web|title=Ethiopia: EU suspends budget support over Tigray conflict|url=https://www.dw.com/en/ethiopia-eu-suspends-budget-support-over-tigray-conflict/a-55944784|access-date=2020-12-17|date=2020-12-16|website=[[Deutsche_Welle|Deutsche Welle]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217222502/https://www.dw.com/en/ethiopia-eu-suspends-budget-support-over-tigray-conflict/a-55944784|archive-date=2020-12-17|quote=Aid access:- The UN Security Council on Monday held an informal meeting on the humanitarian situation in Ethiopia's Tigray region, where the majority of humanitarian organizations are not allowed to enter. A humanitarian crisis is unfolding on such a scale that organizations are afraid of what they will find once allowed in.|url-status=no}}</ref>

至2021年3月13日，联合国和其合作伙伴救助了90万人，给予他们完整的食品篮，70万人获得了纯净水。尽管有所进展，由于进行中的交火，很多人难以接洽。约有450万人仍需救援，其中100万人由于战火而处于无法进入的地区。<ref name=":9">{{Cite journal|title=OCHA: ETHIOPIA – TIGRAY REGION HUMANITARIAN UPDATE|url=https://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/Situation%20Report%20-%20Ethiopia%20-%20Tigray%20Region%20Humanitarian%20Update%20-%2013%20Mar%202021.pdf|journal=[[United_Nations_Office_for_the_Coordination_of_Humanitarian_Affairs|United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs]]|access-date=2021-03-21|archive-date=2021-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318063338/https://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/Situation%20Report%20-%20Ethiopia%20-%20Tigray%20Region%20Humanitarian%20Update%20-%2013%20Mar%202021.pdf|url-status=no}}</ref>

{{tsl|en|World Peace Foundation|世界和平基金會}}於2021年4月表示單計提格雷地區的中部和東部，每日有50至100人由於直接與饑餓相關的原因而死。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.economist.com/graphic-detail/2021/04/22/tigray-is-edging-closer-to-famine |title=Tigray is edging closer to famine |publisher=The Economist |date=2021-04-22 |access-date=2021-10-19 |archive-date=2021-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211028041812/https://www.economist.com/graphic-detail/2021/04/22/tigray-is-edging-closer-to-famine |dead-url=no }}</ref>

聯合國官員在2021年夏天稱提格雷在2020年戰事開始時已遭受蝗災打擊導致失去四分一農作物，剩下的收成又有9成以上被掠奪或被毀。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://news.un.org/zh/story/2021/07/1088852 |title=埃塞俄比亚提格雷地区10万名儿童面临营养不良造成的死亡风险 |work=聯合國新聞 |date=2021-07-30 |accessdate=2021-07-31 |archive-date=2021-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210731042512/https://news.un.org/zh/story/2021/07/1088852 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

據2021年6月的報導，提格雷地區已有兩地各自報告有超過100人[[餓死|餓死]]。同一報導提到有一批援助物資被厄立特里亞軍掠奪。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://apnews.com/article/only-on-ap-united-nations-ethiopia-africa-9540b17507dcb58dd78b79116e6d9aa7 |title=Trapped in Ethiopia's Tigray, people 'falling like leaves' |work=AP News |date=2021-06-30 |accessdate=2021-10-19 |archive-date=2021-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211212162829/https://apnews.com/article/only-on-ap-united-nations-ethiopia-africa-9540b17507dcb58dd78b79116e6d9aa7 |dead-url=no }}</ref>單在2021年8月，另有至少150人餓死。2021年9月中，[[世界糧食計劃署|世界糧食計劃署]]表示自7月12日以來有445輛運載物資的承包商卡車進入提格雷地區，但只有38輛返回，缺乏卡車阻礙了該署的工作，署方不知道其餘卡車的去向。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/9/17/hundreds-aid-trucks-not-returned-ethiopia-tigray-un |title=Hundreds of aid trucks have failed to return from Tigray, UN says |publisher=Al Jazeera |date=2021-09-17 |accessdate=2021-11-01 |archive-date=2021-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211216035626/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/9/17/hundreds-aid-trucks-not-returned-ethiopia-tigray-un |dead-url=no }}</ref>截至2021年9月，已有超過35萬公噸糧食援助抵達埃塞俄比亞，但是在埃塞俄比亞政府的封鎖政策下，只有很少量能夠運到提格雷地區。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.voanews.com/a/i-just-cry-dying-of-hunger-in-ethiopia-s-blockaded-tigray-/6235558.html |title='I Just Cry’: Dying of Hunger in Ethiopia’s Blockaded Tigray |agency=Associated Press |date=2021-09-20 |accessdate=2021-09-21 |archive-date=2021-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211106141912/https://www.voanews.com/a/i-just-cry-dying-of-hunger-in-ethiopia-s-blockaded-tigray-/6235558.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2021年12月有報導稱提格雷部隊掠奪了世界糧食計劃署存放於孔博勒查的大量糧食物資。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-59588956 |title=Ethiopia war: UN halts food aid in two towns after warehouses looted |publisher=BBC |date=2021-12-09 |accessdate=2021-12-09 |archive-date=2021-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211211111111/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-59588956 |dead-url=no }}</ref>12月10日，相信來自埃塞俄比亞國防軍或盟友部隊的人員在孔博勒查強行徵用了糧食計劃署的18輛卡車，後來歸還其中15輛。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.voanews.com/a/wfp-aid-trucks-commandeered-in-northern-ethiopia/6352522.html |title=18 WFP Aid Trucks Commandeered in Northern Ethiopia |publisher=VOA |date=2021-12-13 |accessdate=2021-12-14 |archive-date=2021-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211215231330/https://www.voanews.com/a/wfp-aid-trucks-commandeered-in-northern-ethiopia/6352522.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2022年1月有報導稱在提格雷最大醫院有一些醫護人員已經8個月沒有獲發工資，被迫乞討食物自救。同月聯合國報告稱有220萬人極度缺乏食物。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-60169326 |title=Ethiopia civil war: Doctors among those begging for food in Tigray |publisher=BBC |date=2022-01-28 |accessdate=2022-01-28 |archive-date=2022-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220615035001/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-60169326 }}</ref>


==分析==
在戰爭爆發時，據報埃塞俄比亞軍隊大部分軍事裝備集中於北方司令部。提格雷軍奪取了這些裝備後，在戰爭初期大多被無人機摧毀或是被厄立特里亞軍擄獲，很少裝備能夠再次落入埃軍手中。<ref name=e2>{{cite web |url=https://www.essra.org.cn/view-1000-2969.aspx |title=提格雷战争的进程——蔡德坎•格伯滕萨将军专访（二） |publisher=欧亚系统科学研究会 |date=2021-07-25 |access-date=2021-11-02 |archive-date=2021-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211105031121/https://www.essra.org.cn/view-1000-2969.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

戰前埃塞俄比亞國防軍曾經有約18%的人員是提格雷尼亞人，在軍官團所佔比例更是此數的二倍左右。德·瓦爾認為阿比政府在軍隊推行減少提格雷尼亞人影響力的改革損害了軍隊士氣和凝聚力，而阿比在戰爭爆發前未有足夠時間完成軍隊的重整。<ref name=bbc20211118/>Kjetil Tronvoll認為阿比政府在曾經長期由提格雷尼亞人主導的聯邦軍隊中拘捕大量士兵和軍官的做法，削弱了聯邦軍隊的能力，而埃塞俄比亞國防軍也有大量內部爭鬥。另一方面，提格雷軍有較高的士氣和爭取勝利的決心，提人陣的部隊有紀律，是一群「受過良好教育」的人。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://p.dw.com/p/42eAE |title=What are the chances for peace in Ethiopia's Tigray conflict? |publisher=DW |date=2021-11-06}}</ref>

然而，在阿比政府從國外獲得更多[[無人戰鬥航空載具|戰鬥無人機]]後，從2021年11月底開始，戰場形勢變得對阿比政府有利。據估計截至2021年12月，阿比政府可動用的戰鬥無人機不超過數十架。<ref name=nyt20211220>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/12/20/world/africa/drones-ethiopia-war-turkey-emirates.html |title=Foreign Drones Tip the Balance in Ethiopia’s Civil War |publisher=The New York Times |date=2021-12-20 |accessdate=2021-12-23 |archive-date=2022-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220228162054/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/12/20/world/africa/drones-ethiopia-war-turkey-emirates.html }}</ref>

